But I'll be posting new stuff again next week! So please stay tuned! If you guys want to see more of my longer content, please subscribe to my Ytube channel, link in my bio 🙏 
.
.

Digital illustration and video edits by yours truly
.

Fake VFX: Pixar edition.  Just realized how rarely I do Pixar stuffs. And also I’ve never done CARS related artwork before, so here you go!  Since Lightning was voiced by Owen Wilson, thought it’d be fun to put him on the mix (hence the IG story I posted yesterday.). KACHOW!
.

node.text:
Happy 26th birthday to one of my favorite movies of all time, Clueless! To celebrate this iconic movie, here's a compilation of my Clueless related works from 2017 to 2020.
What's your favorite Clueless quotes? Let me know in the comment section below!
.
Clueless (1995) courtesy of Paramount Pictures
.
Cinderella (1950), The Princess and the Frog (2009) Beauty and The Beast (1991),The Little Mermaid (1989) courtesy of Disney 
.
Legally Blonde (2001) courtesy of MGM
.
Digital illustration and composite by yours truly.
.
